Notes from github

Global setup:
 Download and install Git
  git config --global user.name "Arr Matey"
  git config --global user.email rm8t@me.com
        
Next steps:
  mkdir helloworld
  cd helloworld
  git init
  touch README
  git add README
  git commit -m 'first commit'
  git remote add origin git@github.com:rm8t/helloworld.git
  git push origin master
      
Existing Git Repo?
